  "texts": [
    "As clear from Table 3, the overall classification accuracy of our proposed method is 96.3% on the Eurosat test dataset, which is 7.13%, 2.15%, 2.13%, and 1.55% higher than that of Pretrained Resnet-34 on ImageNet, Pretrained Resnet-34 on ImageNet with Finetunning, MTLN, and Multi-Branch Deep Learning Framework (MBDLF), respectively.",
    "As shown in Fig. 10, it is asserted that the proposed strategy achieves satisfactory accuracy which attains 96.3% accuracy in 10 categories, and most categories obtain more than 95% accuracy.",
    "Features and attention maps visualization on the proposed RCA networkWe aim to focus more on the key image channels, which contain the most distinguishable feature maps, that are crucial for scene categorization.",
